<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #EB8E5F;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d48d6a;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #EB8E5F;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            border-top: 1px solid #d48d6a;
        }
        a {
            color: #EB8E5F;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            color: #d48d6a;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .button-link {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 10px auto;
            background-color: #EB8E5F;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .button-link:hover {
            background-color: #d48d6a;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .refund-details {
            background-color: #ffcccb;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Fatima's Therapy Services</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear Admin,</p>
            <p>{{name}} has submitted a refund request. The cancellation policy requires cancellations to be made within a specific time frame, and this user has adhered to the policy's conditions. Here are the details of the request:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>User Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</li>
                <li><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingId}}</li>
                <li><strong>Event Date and Time:</strong> {{eventDate}} at {{eventTime}}</li>
                <li><strong>Cancelled within policy period?</strong> {{cancelledWithinPolicyPeriod}}</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong> {{paymentAmount}} PKR</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong> {{paymentStatus}} on {{paymentCompleted}}</li>
                <li><strong>Transaction Reference Number:</strong> {{transactionReferenceNumber}}</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="refund-details">
                <p>
                    Please follow these steps to review the payment and process the refund:
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Decide whether to approve or reject the refund request (most likely should)</li>
                    <li>Click the button below to review the payment on Safepay's website (Search by order ID).</li>
                    <li>If you approve the refund request, press the refund button on the Safepay payment details page.</li>
                    <li>If you reject the refund request, please contact the user directly to resolve the issue.</li>
                    <li>[ATTENTION] Ensure that the transaction reference number matches the details provided.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <a href="{{refundLink}}" class="button-link">Review Payment</a>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further information, please contact us directly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            Regards,<br>
            The Finance Team<br>
            <a href="https://www.fatimanaqvi.com">www.fatimanaqvi.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
